67
00:04:57,180 --> 00:05:00,030
- I thought you said no
one came here.

68
00:05:00,030 --> 00:05:01,210
- Yeah, we should go.

69
00:05:10,060 --> 00:05:13,060
(girl giggles)

70
00:05:13,060 --> 00:05:15,000
- I'll see you later.

