92
00:07:38,130 --> 00:07:40,150
- So, how it go with Jen?

93
00:07:42,020 --> 00:07:44,010
- Alright I guess.

94
00:07:44,010 --> 00:07:46,000
- Bet she thinks
you're a weirdo.

95
00:07:46,000 --> 00:07:47,110
